{"tid":811103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"柴灣係咪有棟樓可以上到天台","createTime":"2018-09-08T13:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T15:01:31.000Z","uid":183415,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"73067b222a2d7a6a0ebe4f6c11f0339524c6cb72","tid":811103,"uid":183415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26671f40b7ccefb72b40d197a40030b22b151fc1","tid":811103,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d164f694bae9c8c47fd6c2c9a15fcb4ecb2eac","tid":811103,"uid":67840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"不安"},{"pid":"7ccf2ff545303767cc3243da8331dc31b41a2e08","tid":811103,"uid":95648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"要死死遠d啦 咪撚阻住我返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cdc0818f5c93eace30bc1d0136ca64b222f38c","tid":811103,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"看來你心中的困苦，已令你覺得生無可戀．．．人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=X6rhx2bzFlrsuPJ%2BUbrbMjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7e28dba5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk</a> 。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=X6rhx2bzFlrsuPJ%2BUbrbMjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=327b9e16\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a>）。你更可以進入網站內的『真心話室』（星期一至日，下午８時至凌晨１時）即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"9af6de3716def09614246eded5c9ad5237f23c97","tid":811103,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n叫柴灣ive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1a0e07dd650185bf0d9e7b41f879c516fe51a4","tid":811103,"uid":183415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"聽人講話影相好靚，想去睇下"},{"pid":"19d912c415cbfb8f57b5d9812fb94c316854a7ed","tid":811103,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"}]}